Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.19,0:00:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於前天襲擊\N麥克馬多基地的組織
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詳細情況完全不明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部分人士指稱與前幾天在\N羅斯冰棚發現的巨大氣流體有關
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.14,0:00:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於這項攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.47,0:00:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總統稍早發表了\N"不排除強力反擊"的聲明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.91,0:00:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接到這項消息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.84,0:00:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南半球各國的緊張情勢升高
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.28,0:00:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未確認消息指出\N部分區域因恐慌而發生暴動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外，現在依然無法恢復\N與麥克馬多基地的通訊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.12,0:00:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今人對基地的安危感到憂心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.73,0:00:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著即將轉播總統發表的記者會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.63,0:00:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請在電視機前稍候片刻...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.48,0:01:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是本機動艦隊司令官南雲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.01,0:01:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天很榮幸能見到\N這麼多新聞媒體人士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.32,0:01:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本軍在這個時期派遣\N大規模艦隊的目的是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.39,0:01:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有人說這是想成為\N常任理事國的示威行動...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.46,0:01:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我軍只是履行政府基於\N聯合國正式請託所做的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.70,0:01:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟防衛南極是人類共同的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.28,0:01:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這項任務是以\N跟迦姆作戰為前提嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.31,0:01:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的任務是防衛"通路"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.72,0:01:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防衛對象是針對由地球外\N通過通路而來的所有敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.46,0:01:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.49,0:01:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請說說身為下期\N聯合國幹事國的抱負
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.63,0:01:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞洲各國抱持強烈警戒心\N您對這件事有什麼看法呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.10,0:02:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解，UN-401
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是V-09
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.44,0:02:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在將前往定點33\N進行海上巡邏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.41,0:02:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK，V-09  了解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.21,0:02:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo Charlie Delta Echo，這裡是提督\N請飛向C-080  結束
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.02,0:02:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了，那群人終於走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.09,0:02:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下就能清靜點...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉，傑克森小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.13,0:02:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起\N讓我一個人可以留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不...千萬別這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.87,0:02:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是向妳展現\N我軍行動的大好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.74,0:02:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，我會好好觀察的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.71,0:02:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我就是為此而來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠如各位所知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.67,0:04:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方所導入的新技術與\N新兵器屢次遭迦姆複製
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到目前為止\N戰況都是一進一退的膠著狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以過去的攻擊方法來說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先由戰略偵查軍團所做的觀測\N來確認迦姆基地的所在位置
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.15,0:04:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再進行空襲和轟炸來予以牽制\N是我軍的基本戰略
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對此，迦姆卻由\N完全不同方向的據點出現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.46,0:04:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我方的背後襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.77,0:04:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個模式出現了許多次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據中央電腦依據\N最新觀測結果所做的分析
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.61,0:04:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些迦姆基地的配對\N有一定的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:04:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南極？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，跟深井中尉一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.72,0:05:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要選在這種時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SUPER PHOENIX Mk. XI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.09,0:05:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要對B-3換裝的新發動機\N進行燃燒測試
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在地球大氣圈內
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.38,0:05:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經連絡地球那邊了，所以不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.89,0:05:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會突然被砲擊的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，上校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來向各位說明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是系統軍團開發的\N強化裝甲系統BAX-4
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將以此編成實戰部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在對兩大據點"餅乾"及"有錢的男孩"\N進行大規模轟炸後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.77,0:06:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投入該部隊\N從地面壓制迦姆的據點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外，關於地面戰力的要員
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.15,0:06:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會從各戰隊中\N因座機遭擊落而多出的人員裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以"再教育"的名目招集
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,編成一支臨時部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.03,0:06:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在製作名單
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.83,0:06:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B-3，這裡是油管操作員
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油即將結束，保持現在的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.94,0:06:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(加油中)\N(連結油槽)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.01,0:06:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油結束，拔出油管
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.11,0:06:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解，收回受油口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你好運，回力鏢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.95,0:06:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝，牛奶1號，祝你好運
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:06:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回力鏢...啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.43,0:07:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在做嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.34,0:07:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，這次做的成品感覺不錯喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是學不乖的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是很深奧的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前我做了一支完美的成品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.82,0:07:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞了單晶片的人工智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超大型積體電路的...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.86,0:07:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音苦澀透了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.93,0:07:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子都聽得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.38,0:07:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縫了三針
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.21,0:07:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機器這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.55,0:07:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要自然地在空中飛舞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.62,0:07:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在嫌太過死板了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:08:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰爭結束後，你有什麼打算？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒想過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你又有什麼打算？傑克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.87,0:08:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到故鄉當個老百姓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，我找個機會\N帶你到我故鄉去一趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是個除了田地\N其它什麼都沒有的地方...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.41,0:08:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想在那裡丟回力鏢嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，讓你見識我的得意作品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.93,0:08:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,測站氣壓(QNH)快速下降
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再60秒進入通路(IP)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.30,0:08:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛入航線
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃料
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,18.0
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢查警告燈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢查，沒有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.11,0:08:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氧氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氧氣檢查OK
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.28,0:08:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,油壓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.24,0:08:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排氣溫度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.65,0:08:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,800度，正常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(敵我識別系統：敵人)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三點鐘方向有敵機
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.42,0:08:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TYPE2，三架
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:08:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝通路過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，巡邏的傢伙們在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.32,0:09:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零，擊落他們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.63,0:09:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣衝進去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們居然帶了這麼棘手的禮物來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再20秒進入通路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.34,0:09:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指示空速500節
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.61,0:09:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢查機體帶電壓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從300毫伏特(mV)開始上升
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,0:09:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認入口，進入
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.96,0:09:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三架？會不會是固定回波？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟報告不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.90,0:09:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝向警戒區過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.67,0:09:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊退他們，老鷹1號、2號
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.20,0:09:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老鷹1號、2號了解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷹眼呼叫提督56
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.08,0:09:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與報告不同，FAF機有三架
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:09:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於已靠近警戒空域
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.58,0:10:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派老鷹前往迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是提督，了解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認目標，一點鐘方向下方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.49,0:10:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是隸屬聯合國軍的\N日本海軍機
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.73,0:10:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通告FAF
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴機將飛離事前通告的飛行區域
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員展開對空戰鬥部署
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.84,0:10:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員展開對空戰鬥部署
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.41,0:10:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老鷹、飛龍各隊立刻出動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎擊不明機
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員展開對空戰鬥部署
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.35,0:10:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員展開對空戰鬥部署
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.68,0:10:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老鷹、飛龍各隊立刻出動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.96,0:10:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通告FAF機
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻解除武裝，並且跟隨我們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.83,0:10:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是隸屬聯合國軍的\N日本海軍機
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是包圍我們的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:10:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們會成為迦姆的祭品喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請解除武裝並且跟隨我們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再重複一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FAF機，我們是日本海軍機\N隸屬於聯合國軍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.92,0:11:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被攔截了，請解除武裝並且跟隨我們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.12,0:11:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明機三架
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.12,0:11:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正高速接近本艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.92,0:11:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攔截機呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離接觸還有約10分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全艦，對空飛彈發射
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對空飛彈發射
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.33,0:11:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全艦，發射對空飛彈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.40,0:11:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全艦，發射對空飛彈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.25,0:11:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球艦隊發射了飛彈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.95,0:11:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來會被他們逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航空母艦竟然在那麼近的地方...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.19,0:11:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零，擊落他們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.79,0:11:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃料不夠，會回不去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.76,0:11:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係，不管怎樣都要解決他們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.94,0:12:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.44,0:12:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行追擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.31,0:12:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛龍3號，失去聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.64,0:12:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛龍3號、4號被擊落
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.14,0:12:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往老家過去了，快追擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.14,0:12:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}("老家"在這裡指航空母艦"提督56")
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.59,0:12:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標接近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:13:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電子反制(ECM)嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.56,0:13:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.78,0:13:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球的那些傢伙沒辦法嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了，在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.72,0:13:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的目標是航空母艦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.76,0:13:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個發動機測試任務還真不賴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(衝壓進氣模式)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往這裡過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.78,0:13:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算撞過去也要阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:13:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一架，從左舷過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.63,0:14:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.09,0:14:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鈞一髮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.92,0:14:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壽命都縮短了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑克\N(燃料不足)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去要泡海水澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.47,0:14:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃料多的是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.34,0:14:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:14:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有國際條約
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.51,0:14:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不許他們說不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本艦呼叫老鷹5號
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.28,0:15:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷹眼2號，中止著艦\N緊急通訊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃料？\N立刻中止進場
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在立刻派加油機過去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.49,0:15:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，FAF要緊急著艦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把甲板全部空出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外星人要登場了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.24,0:15:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋，高度太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.21,0:15:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.54,0:15:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，會墜落的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.98,0:15:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,側寫？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把迦姆當成一個人的人格嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，希望妳分析出他們的下一步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這會變成我主觀視點的分析喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.58,0:16:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，怎麼突然想到要做這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.19,0:16:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管再怎麼地機械化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人類參予的戰爭\N是不可能存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.73,0:16:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這是只有對我們而言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.97,0:16:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦姆過去都只將我們人類製造的\N機械與電腦視為敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而現在...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.95,0:16:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻改變戰略\N將目標鎖定為人類了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.52,0:16:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，在這個從作戰立案到\N管理預算都交給電腦的軍隊裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.90,0:17:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們開始將焦點鎖定在\N"人類"這個不確定要素上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.34,0:17:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代表戰術知性體已經被...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.11,0:17:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道... 怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想存活下去的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對什麼事情都要有所注意喔\N伊蒂絲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了，拜託妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.19,0:18:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是盛大的歡迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.77,0:18:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是宣傳班的石川
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於您要求的燃料補給
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.54,0:18:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正透過聯合國\N與FAF進行照會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要確認法規符合
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.51,0:18:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便立刻開始作業
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.88,0:18:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝您的顧慮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是FAF特殊戰的\N詹姆斯·波克少校
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能幫我引見艦隊司令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.72,0:18:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.82,0:18:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.67,0:18:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們打算不理我們到什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說是不得已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.01,0:18:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不小心把他們也捲了進來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.19,0:19:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此時若還要他們說\N"歡迎光臨地球"是很難的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.56,0:19:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是我們攻擊他們的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對這裡的人而言
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰打的都差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.23,0:19:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是只有特殊戰才有的\N特別機組吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FRX-00
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經正式配備\N改叫FRX-44MR了，是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.31,0:19:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有你們的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.25,0:20:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船也很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.31,0:20:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝，我向你們道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.52,0:20:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問您是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.82,0:20:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是琳·傑克森
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.92,0:20:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是個記者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.70,0:20:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，"入侵者"...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.50,0:20:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是光榮\N竟然能讓FAF的人看過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.94,0:20:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是本好書
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.54,0:20:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一件很有意義的工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.21,0:20:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是詹姆斯·波克
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.71,0:20:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深井 零
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.72,0:20:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這架雪風的駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.35,0:20:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪風
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽起來的感覺真是不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是像綽號一樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.33,0:20:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您來這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.76,0:20:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，是為了取材
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的話\N能否稍微請教一些...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.21,0:21:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令答應要見您
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.58,0:21:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶您到司令室去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.51,0:21:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.21,0:21:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，待會見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.56,0:21:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得你們回到了地球
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.00,0:21:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的地球人，大家都是那種感覺喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.23,0:21:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦姆明明就近在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.37,0:21:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻連那迦姆的存在\N都拿來當作自己鬥爭的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.64,0:21:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽妳這種講法...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.88,0:21:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺妳好像不是地球人似的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.95,0:21:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.02,0:21:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，你也簡直像是個外星人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.23,0:21:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起話來聲音還蠻好聽的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.09,0:22:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.59,0:22:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這麼堅持...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.60,0:22:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候對於在新聞影片中\N第一次看到的迦姆感到非常恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.58,0:22:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想知道自己\N所害怕的東西到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做各種調查時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.25,0:22:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺就...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.72,0:22:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連家人都不想理我了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.86,0:23:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是過去大家也都還吵著說\N"這是人類的危機"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.70,0:23:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在好像全都忘光了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.40,0:23:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記了在"通路"彼方\N一顆名為菲雅利的外星球上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.27,0:23:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭依然持續著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.55,0:23:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，迦姆是實際存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.05,0:23:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為現實帶來了威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.49,0:23:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要與這種異質的敵人對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.63,0:23:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能勇敢面對他們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.86,0:23:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為根本沒有地方...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.83,0:23:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.49,0:25:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也有失望的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.89,0:25:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我還抱持著希望
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.80,0:25:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信人類沒有那麼愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.23,0:25:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也許還看不見週遭
